                <p>My first encounter with software development came in Sixth Form at Sutton Coldfield College. Over a number of lessons we were introduced to Visual Basic 6 and worked towards building a simple calculator application. I immediately saw the potential of what we were doing and wanted to add more beyond simple addition, subtraction, multiplication and division. </p>
