                <p>After brushing up my skills and aquainting myself with the Microsoft .Net Framework, I managed to get my first professional developer job at Cuskit Limited. When I arrived, Cuskit was a business built around a bespoke ERP system originally written in Informix 4GL that had been ported to VB6 and was in dire need of modernisation. My first major role was to facilitate the porting of that system into VB.Net in order to bring more modern interfaces for the users and allow us developers to move past the limitations of the very dated VB6.</p>
